Wonderstruck is a Freshmen Orientation Camp formed under the collaboration of both NUS Muslim Society and NUS Malay Language Society. It will be held on 2 separate periods. First, a one-day e-camp in July, focusing on intra-faculty bonding. Second, it will span over 2 days in August, focusing on inter-faculty bonding. Through online games and activities, the camp aims to orientate the freshmen on the resources available in NUS and to also foster bonding and friendship amongst them.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
